metadata.name: Alpha Kongs Club - AKC #14
metadata.description:
An Exclusive Club of 8,888 Alpha Kongs, made by the lead visual artists behind Star Wars, Game of Thrones, Harry Potter, Pokémon and more.

Membership will grant access to the first NFT festivals in history with famous artists, the exclusive Blue Banana Serum, Omega Kongs NFT, partnerships, voting rights in the community’s future and more. Get in while you still can.

More info at (https://alphakongsclub.com/)
